Dynmark,is,a,cloud,based,system,that,powers,mobile,messaging,services,It,enables,users,to,send,single,or,batch,SMS,messages,send,delayed,messages,receive,SMS,messages,forward,messages,to,email,search,message,archives,and,even,set,hours,appropriate,for,receiving,messages,Dynmark,s,Cloud,Portal,is,highly,customizable,and,can,be,readily,configured,to,include,the,desired,widgets,and,information,The,service,can,also,be,used,and,configured,programmatically,via,SOAP,API